Package: RGremlinsConjoint
Type: Package
Title: Estimate the "Gremlins in the Data" Model for Conjoint Studies
Version: 0.5.0
Author: John Howell, Peter Ebbes, and John Leichty
Maintainer: John Howell <john_howell@byu.edu>
Description: The gremlins package provides the tools and utilities to estimate a the model described in
  "Gremlin's in the Data: Identifying the Information Content of Research Subjects" using
  conjoint analysis data such as that collected in Sawtooth Software's Lighthouse or Discover
  Products.  The packages also contains utility functions for formating the input data and
  extracting the relevant results.
